      • contains

        public boolean contains(Point point,
                        int totalPointBoxSize)
        Function for checking if the Line instance contains a Point.
        Parameters:
        point - the Point that is going to be checked for.
        totalPointBoxSize - the total size of the box around the Point that is used in order to check if the Line contains it. The larger the total size, the further the Point can be away from the Line.
        Returns:
        true if the Point is on the Line, otherwise false.
